column4:
Whoah whoah whoah. Okay before you go off shoving that shit in your arm do a taste test. Does it taste like dope? Even before that do a smell test, you should know that vinegary smelly by now. Okay so it if smells (kinda) and tastes like dope, go ahead and snort a little. Did it do anything to you? If so... I don't think it's cooking up blue/green but more of a darkish hue of grey. I want to see a picture because that's interesting if it's real dope and it looks blue/green.

At first thought I said, hmm looks like dirt/some bs filler. Then I thought who in the fuck would sell H in little rocks like that, I mean look at it, there's no powder there it's all in rock form even the tiny bits. 

Might no be real, but if it is please do be careful OP. We got some shit that looked kinda similar and cooked up greyish, I can send you a pic if you want. And it was very strong (as in I do .5g shots and I only needed .03. That's not even half a point) to get high. And I mean fucking high. 

Edit: I hope OP is okay, in all seriousness this shit always concerns me. Fucking dealers.

Found this: http://forum.opiophile.org/archive/index.php/t-22857.html  
  
Might be a fent analog?

Wow littlemouse this is so weird because I just picked up some black/green stuff too. Did you put heat on it? When I did the rocks became suuuuuper soft and the shot was very dark. I got a major rush though but I wonder if they have a similar cut or something.

I got very dark / greenish stuff that looked almost like this a few days ago. I had never seen shit that color. Fortunately it still got me high, and it was actually pretty good. The color was just so weird!
i had some shit like that before turned out to be tamper proof oxy like it gets dark dark green to where u can bearley see the blood right

I got some shit that looked exactly like that. Broke down real cloudy/milky. Had to heat it to be able to draw it up. I tasted it first before injecting it, and it definantly tasted like heroin. The high wasn't real good tho, and didn't have any legs to speak of. It also got really dark tan after putting heat on it.
Does not get me high. At all. :(
http://i.imgur.com/IU790h7.jpg
I was gonna say fent analog if it worked for her. Too bad it didn't and it's just shitty shit.
It doesn't get me high. At all. Just barely not sick.
Why is your username so familiar?
Verdict: BUNK. Sorry :( it happens. Please don't shoot it.
[deleted]
I. Love. That. Polish. I dunno what that shit is. I had some heroin that was a light blue color one time, many moons ago. It was decent shit.

That's what the OP in the Opiophile thread said.  
  
>SWIM slammed about half of one of these bags twice already and it helped her stave off the WDs but she didn't really get high..
I could be asking you the same thing :P
Yeah, I mean... I just kind of want to know what the fuck it is. Just out of morbid curiosity. It gets rid of all WD symptoms so it is something....
I honestly injected nearly half a gram of this shit before making this post... I'll shoot anything. I'm awful.
Yup. I came here to say I used to get some pretty damn good blue tinted shit that was cool for the novelty of it. Cool way of branding but now that I shoot it I wouldn't enjoy it as much.
I read the wrong thing. But yeah, that's my same experience and it makes me want to cry.
A mystery then...
I'm gonna go with Fent Analog. Remember that shit that was killing all those people? Well this is like the exact opposite of that.
Haha in true junkie fashion. I'm the same way. Though I hope nothing bad happens to you from it
Sorry mouse, better luck next time. :\
I think that I've seen you on tinychat before? I used to go in there a lot, but haven't lately due to my laptop being a piece of shit.
It brings the dead back to life? Oh fuck.

A fent analogue is not ever that color...
Its most likely a crushed up pill.

Fent will NEVER look like that. I see a lot of people using the word 'fentanyl' like its nothing since the ODs on the east coast. In reality you'll rarely get fent as dope.
And that would be my luck exactly
Oh yeah, that was it. My laptop was a piece of shot too so I'm never on anymore either.

Not that color drawn up, I've never seen that shit either. Doesn't mean it's not a shitty fent analog which just happens to be shit and filled with bs that makes it turn blue/green. Fucking weird case here, though. It's not really baffling if you think about it entirely, because it's just bunk that happens to turn that color.
